snippet.title: PV Part 1 of "Jujutsu Kaisen Phantom Parade" |   the official mobile game of "Jujutsu Kaisen"
snippet.description:
The global version of the game is set to launch in 2024. Stay tuned!
Players, are you ready to fight alongside characters like Yuji Itadori and Satoru Gojo and enter the world of jujutsu?!

Game pre-registration is now available, register here: 
App Store:https://apps.apple.com/us/app/id6475925341
Google Play:https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bilibilihk.jujutsuphanparagp
Official Website:https://jujutsuphanpara.biligames.com/

#jujutsukaisen 
#phantomparade
